 Do not use imports from `@remix-run`, use `react-router` instead.
 Do not import `json` from `react-router` use `data` instead, and only if we are returning response status or headers.
 Use `loaderData` and `actionData` from `Route.ComponentProps` as the data from a route component instead of `useLoaderData` or `useActionData`.
 When using `<Link />` and `<Button />` always wrap the link inside the button and use `asChild` for the button.

